HEADWORD: Prevertebral
<hw>Pre*ver"te*bral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated immediately in front, or on the ventral side, of the
vertebral column; prespinal.</def>⟦br⟧
